name: Logic55
overview:
Crookless.com is bringing technology to market that will allow parties to safely and securely connect to each other via online marketplaces, while eliminating the need to expose their personal contact information.

Likewise, Crookless.com technology will defeat the efforts of fraudsters and predatory marketers to contact unsuspecting parties in bulk, looking for their next mark. They will also lose the ability to victimize without leaving trails of forensic data for law enforcement to use in apprehending them.
